    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>令人满足的清洁体验</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感受水流的压力，看着浓厚的泡沫覆盖污垢。画面与音效都经过精心设计，让每一次清洗都充满成就感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111030/extras/162a609670fb14f1c0c08f80d666330c.poster.avif?t=1771662948\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111030/extras/162a609670fb14f1c0c08f80d666330c.webm?t=1771662948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111030/extras/162a609670fb14f1c0c08f80d666330c.mp4?t=1771662948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>车间与自定义</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扩展你的业务。开启车间更换轮胎，或使用定制区域为任何车辆贴上独特的贴纸。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111030/extras/c113a8e5c27c509681da08efd5acd0c7.poster.avif?t=1771662948\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111030/extras/c113a8e5c27c509681da08efd5acd0c7.webm?t=1771662948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111030/extras/c113a8e5c27c509681da08efd5acd0c7.mp4?t=1771662948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>卡牌收集系统</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在工作中获得随机车辆卡牌。完成套组即可解锁标志性车型，并吸引更多顾客前来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111030/extras/7b07979a39442c79d2b27498514c235b.poster.avif?t=1771662948\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111030/extras/7b07979a39442c79d2b27498514c235b.webm?t=1771662948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111030/extras/7b07979a39442c79d2b27498514c235b.mp4?t=1771662948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>阻止小偷</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >并非每个人都会付钱。当顾客试图逃跑时，使用网球发射器，通过基于物理的布娃娃效果将他们制服。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111030/extras/706c1c3da9a3f1fd8ed967bd97aa1a89.poster.avif?t=1771662948\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111030/extras/706c1c3da9a3f1fd8ed967bd97aa1a89.webm?t=1771662948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111030/extras/706c1c3da9a3f1fd8ed967bd97aa1a89.mp4?t=1771662948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>关爱你的顾客</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >别忘了让顾客满意，以维持你的生意！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>他们的快乐就是你的快$$！</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111030/extras/5b8dbf47c536731dcb377839a2140856.poster.avif?t=1771662948\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111030/extras/5b8dbf47c536731dcb377839a2140856.webm?t=1771662948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111030/extras/5b8dbf47c536731dcb377839a2140856.mp4?t=1771662948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111030/extras/22759e8b32e671cbc35c0e82a5d514c2.poster.avif?t=1771662948\" width=780 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111030/extras/22759e8b32e671cbc35c0e82a5d514c2.webm?t=1771662948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111030/extras/22759e8b32e671cbc35c0e82a5d514c2.mp4?t=1771662948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>收音机</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 Lofi、80 年代流行乐或阿拉贝斯克之间切换，为你的工作时段营造氛围。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111030/extras/ab4ec7e11130da00f0b209c2459d1f17.poster.avif?t=1771662948\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111030/extras/ab4ec7e11130da00f0b209c2459d1f17.webm?t=1771662948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111030/extras/ab4ec7e11130da00f0b209c2459d1f17.mp4?t=1771662948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>使用彩色肥皂洗车！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >享受绚丽多彩泡沫带来的满足视觉体验！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111030/extras/80b0f24fbee36a824d237991f39e6d80.poster.avif?t=1771662948\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111030/extras/80b0f24fbee36a824d237991f39e6d80.webm?t=1771662948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111030/extras/80b0f24fbee36a824d237991f39e6d80.mp4?t=1771662948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
